{"tid":1902753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegraph電訊報 : 如英超因肺炎而縮短賽程，利物浦或無法被授予英超冠軍銜頭","createTime":"2020-02-28T13:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T14:53:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34ec332fd936ecd472a9067ed3952957c4a2357a","tid":1902753,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9BunpdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9BunpdO.jpg&h=34dfe567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTelegraph電訊報報導：如果英超由於新冠肺炎疫情被縮短賽程，利物浦有可能無法被授予英超冠軍銜頭，也不保證墊底三支球隊不會降班，因為英格蘭足總並沒有處理這種情況的單行條例。<br />\n<br />\n病毒的快速傳播，可能促使英國政府取消至少兩個月的所有體育活動，這會使有些英超比賽無法進行。"},{"pid":"90fb59a150d41f4b225b5be681ee8ebcfe4a073a","tid":1902753,"uid":5191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中國"},{"pid":"aff1f1572cdd2c247a183823b5fff42703d8247a","tid":1902753,"uid":30751,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"就係你地利狗唔識輸波<br />\n先搞到香港咁亂,世界咁亂<br />\n唔比冠軍獎盃你地係彰顯公義,還世人一個公道"},{"pid":"3353509abbb7de684e4f90203a0ae16850052397","tid":1902753,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff1f1572cdd2c247a183823b5fff42703d8247a","tid":1902753,"uid":30751,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"就係你地利狗唔識輸波<br />\n先搞到香港咁亂,世界咁亂<br />\n唔比冠軍獎盃你地係彰顯公義,還世人一個公道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"98e68033d2181bd344e3385260e37adb6d92ffb3","tid":1902753,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278a5e0e1db6294fc9ecacb71a0aa8ea734ef6b9","tid":1902753,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"利記無緣英超冠軍"},{"pid":"48e1fbefb38a9af68bedd5613482de875c008c9c","tid":1902753,"uid":273